comments: Gobert (MIN) slightly extends his arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Wembanyama's (SAS) front as the two come together during the screen.
Alexander-Walker (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests Vassell's (SAS) jump shot to the side of him.
Gobert (MIN) quickly re-establishes his screening position in Sochan's (SAS) path, and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Vassell (SAS) does not give a step of distance as he attempts to establish himself in Gobert's (MIN) path, and illegal contact occurs that affects his ability to defend.
Gobert (MIN) extends his left arm into Wembanyama's (SAS) side and initiates illegal contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Sochan (SAS) slides his hand off Gobert (MIN) as he moves around the pick, and the contact is marginal.
Gobert (MIN) extends his left hand slightly toward Wembanyama (SAS), and marginal contact occurs as Wembanyama moves to defend the shot.
Towns (MIN) jumps alongside Sochan (SAS) as he contests the driving shot attempt, and marginal contact occurs as he grazes Sochan's shoulder after his release.
McDaniels (MIN) reaches in and comes across Johnson's (SAS) arm and shoulder, affecting his SQBR after securing the rebound.
Sochan (SAS) moves forward toward Edwards (MIN) when marginal body contact occurs before Edwards passes.
Wembanyama (SAS) closes out into Towns' (MIN) space and incidental foot contact occurs as the two come together at the start of the drive.
Johnson (SAS) legally contests Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
